rows.label: tev062401_MSG0001
rows.name:
Very dangerous types are skulking about on west
side of Lake Ciel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0002
rows.name:
Nana and friends tend to avoid area
thereabouts for just that reason.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0003
rows.name:
Big friend look stronger than most, but friend should
still be careful if planning to pass through.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0004
rows.name:
After all, friend needs to come home safe and spend
small fortune at shop of Nana![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0009
rows.name: Nana is like jack-of-all-trades here in Dopang Caravan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0010
rows.name:
Might Nana recommend the latest and greatest to
discerning customer like friend?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0011
rows.name:
This yabuyabu ointment was found locally, and can be
yours for absurdly low price of only 1,000,000 credits![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0012
rows.name:
...Meh? Not interested? Friend must not understand
market very well. This is going rate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0013
rows.name: Nana need to find new friend with looser purse strings.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0018
rows.name:
Once, Ganglion in Hilal Stronghold to west came here
to pick fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0019
rows.name:
They start ranting and raving about how Nana and
friends need to surrender. Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0020
rows.name:
So Nana just pretend to surrender, then sell Ganglion
useless junk at ridiculously high prices.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0021
rows.name: Bad guys are very strong, but not very smart.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0026
rows.name:
Such sizzling battle! Every Nopon watched with bated
breath.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0027
rows.name:
Was that friend fighting with giant robot?
Next time, friend need to tell Nana in advance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0028
rows.name:
That way Nana can whip up crowd and make them
pay through nose for snacks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0033
rows.name: Nana hear all about fall of Ganglion![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0034
rows.name:
This is big relief. Nana was making up products like
"toughen-up fruit" and "heal-it-all grass" and selling
them to Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0035
rows.name:
Good thing they all died before finding out products
were bogus![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0036
rows.name:
Actually, both fruit and grass give friends the runs.
So maybe bogus food killed Ganglion...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG0037
rows.name:
Human friends should be thanking Nana for vital role
in major victory! Meh-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG1001
rows.name: Hello, friend! How can jack-of-all-trades Nana help?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG1002
rows.name:
Maybe friend would like to be proud owner of all new
super-starchy dress that Kuta try to dump on Nana?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG1003
rows.name:
Dress is probably too small for friend,
but would make truly lovely hat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG1004
rows.name:
And it can belong to friend for low price of ONLY
1,000,000 credits! Act now! Supply so limited![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG2001
rows.name:
Nana try to scam lovey-dovey newlyweds into
buying surplus junk...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG2002
rows.name:
Uh, Nana mean that Nana want to give Nio first dibs
on extra-special products![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG2003
rows.name:
But Popo forbid Nio from wasting money,
so Nio stop buying from Nana.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG2004
rows.name:
Why did Nio have to marry sensible Nopon?!
What will Nana do now that biggest chump has
put away loose wallet for good? Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062401_MSG2005
rows.name:
Kuta put Nana in major pickle by bringing Nana so
many useless products to sell. Kuta need more
discerning eye for market![ST:wait ]
